ev_ch_Energy = ev_ch_mean['Energy Consumed (kWh)'].mean()
ev_ch_Charging_R = ev_ch_mean['Charging Rate (kW)'].mean()
ev_ch_Distance = ev_ch_mean['Distance Driven (since last charge) (km)'].mean()

print("ค่าเฉลี่ย Energy Consumed (kWh) = ",ev_ch_Energy)
print("ค่าเฉลี่ย Charging Rate (kW) = ",ev_ch_Charging_R)
print("ค่าเฉลี่ย Distance Driven (since last charge) (km) = ",ev_ch_Distance)

ev_ch_mean['Energy Consumed (kWh)'] = ev_ch_mean['Energy Consumed (kWh)'].fillna(ev_ch_Energy)
ev_ch_mean['Charging Rate (kW)'] = ev_ch_mean['Charging Rate (kW)'].fillna(ev_ch_Charging_R)
ev_ch_mean['Distance Driven (since last charge) (km)'] = ev_ch_mean['Distance Driven (since last charge) (km)'].fillna(ev_ch_Distance)

axes[0].set_title('Distribution of Charging Sessions by Location' )
axes[0].set_xlabel('Location')
axes[0].set_ylabel('Count of Charging Sessions' )
axes[0].tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)

sns.countplot(ax=axes[1], data=ev_ch_mean, x='Vehicle Model',palette="viridis")
axes[1].set_title("Vehicle Model of Total Number")
axes[1].set_xlabel("Model")
axes[1].set_ylabel("Number of cars")
axes[1].tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)

axes[2].set_xlabel('Charger Type')
axes[2].set_ylabel('Count of Charging Sessions')
axes[2].tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

sns.countplot(data=ev_ch_mean, x='Vehicle Model', palette="rocket", ax=axes[0, 0])

axes[1, 1].set_ylabel('Charging Duration (hours)')

user_counts = ev_ch_mean['User Type'].value_counts()
